org.universAAL.ucc.profile.agent

Interface ProfileAgent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProfileAgentImpl

    public interface ProfileAgent
    Interface for the actual profile storage and retrieval. Implementations of this interface go in org.universAAL.ucc.profile.agent.impl package; this way the actual storage of profiles can be expanded to other methods and service providers can select from these methods the one that fits best and has best performance, or they can implement their own storage method.
